name: Bunker DAO
description:
Raising funds to buy bunkers in multiple countries. 
We are active in multiple countries in Europe. For every country we aim to raise 200 ETH each. Every funding cycle represents one country. The community will make all the decisions together with Snapshot.

As of 22 Feb: Germany, Sweden, Holland, France and Poland.

Join our movement today, we open our Discord for the public when we reach 100 contributors on Juicebox. 
Other European countries can be added on request.
